Package co.cask.coopr.cluster

Cluster and Node objects.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Cluster Represents a cluster of machines.
Cluster.Builder Builds a cluster object.
ClusterDetails Full cluster details, including the cluster object itself, all nodes in the cluster, and the progress of the last job performed on the cluster.
ClusterJobProgress Summary of the progress of a ClusterJob.
ClusterService Service for performing operations on clusters.
ClusterSummary Summary of a Cluster, used in responding to REST API calls.
Node Represents a machine in a cluster.
Node.Action Defines an action on a node.
NodeProperties Properties of a node.
NodeProperties.Builder Builder for creating node properties.
 

Enum Summary
Cluster.Status Cluster status.
Node.Status Node status.
 

Exception Summary
MissingFieldsException An exception indicating there are required fields that are missing.
